Annotate your query with these hints :

     @QueryHints(value = {
            @QueryHint(name = HINT_FETCH_SIZE, value = &quot;&quot; + Integer.MIN_VALUE),
            @QueryHint(name = HINT_CACHEABLE, value = &quot;false&quot;),
            @QueryHint(name = READ_ONLY, value = &quot;true&quot;)
    })
    @Query(nativeQuery = true, &quot;SELECT t.name, t.date FROM MY_TABLE t WHERE t.condition = true&quot;)
    Stream&lt;MyEntity&gt; getAll();

This will disable second level caching and return read only record.

